summary: Retextures and adds depth to farmhouse roofs.
descriptionHtml:
[center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode][color=#6fa8dc][size=5]What is This?[/size][/color][/font][/center][center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode][size=3][color=#d8d8d8]This mod adds parallax(depth) and retextures farmhouse roofs.
[/color][color=#d8d8d8]After losing my faith while trying to add parallax to Cover Woods, I gave a shot to roofs and it worked![/color][/size][/font][/center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode]
[/font][center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode][color=#6fa8dc][size=5]How to Install?[/size][/color][/font][/center][center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode][color=#d8d8d8][size=3]Automatically with manager or pro manual users know what to do.[/size][/color]
[/font][/center]
